  "texts": [
    "This task involves extracting opinions in a review sentence.",
    "In this example, the opinion term is \"great\".",
    "OTE involves identifying expressions that convey opinions toward a specific aspect or category.",
    "As opinion terms and aspect terms typically co-occur, extracting the opinion term without considering its associated aspect is useless.",
    "Therefore, most existing OTE methods can be decomposed into two sub-tasks: Aspect-Opinion Co-Extraction (AOOE) and Aspect-Oriented Opinion Extraction (AOCE)."
  ],
